snippet.title: AMBER Alert issued for abducted child from Wayne Co., Illinois
snippet.description:
AMBER Alert issued for abducted child from Wayne Co., IllinoisWAYNE CO., Ill. (WTWO/WAWV) — The Wayne County Sheriff’s Office has confirmed a child abduction that occurred at 313 Washington St, Keenes, Illinois.

Alli J Matthews is a female white 9 year old, 4 feet tall, 90 pounds, with brown hair and blue eyes. She is wearing a blue nightgown and pink shoes. Alli was last seen by her father at approximately 6:45 p.m. Friday at their residence was taken from the residence by Teresa A Hill. Ms Hill is 59 yeard old, 5 feet 2 inches tall and weighs 190 pounds, and has blond hair and blue eyes. Teresa Hill is driving a teal 2012 Ford Focus with Indiana license 2 9 0 R V IAnyone with information should call 9 1 1. This concludes this AMBER Alert issued by the Illinois State Police
